parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause a fire, potentially leading to vehicle damage, injury, or even death. In addition, it can also prevent the vehicle from starting, leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Smoke or flames coming from the ignition switch
difficulty or inability to start the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration and brake failure can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as the vehicle may continue to accelerate or fail to stop, making it difficult for the driver to control the vehicle.
symptoms: the vehicle accelerates in open throttle position
the brakes do not engage when pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the master cylinder can cause extended stopping distance, brake failure, and unintended acceleration, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes feel soft or spongy
the brakes do not engage when pressed
the vehicle accelerates in open throttle position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The mislabeling of oil containers can lead to incorrect fluid usage, causing damage to the engine and transmission, potentially resulting in costly repairs or even total loss of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure due to Incorrect Fluid Usage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Using the wrong transmission fluid can cause extensive damage to the transmission, leading to costly repairs or replacement, and potentially resulting in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: slipping or hesitation when shifting gears

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire tread separation can lead to loss of control, accidents, and damage to other vehicle components, such as the muffler, which can result in costly repairs and compromise vehicle safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Muffler Damage Due to Tire Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Damage to the muffler can lead to decreased vehicle performance, increased noise levels, and potentially cause further damage to other exhaust system components, resulting in additional repair costs.
symptoms: Loud noise from the exhaust system

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shutdown of the fuel injection system can cause a loss of power steering, brakes, and engine, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on busy highways.
symptoms: the power steering and brakes become inoperable
the vehicle cannot be restarted due to the location of the restart switch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended shutdown of the fuel injection system can cause a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during sudden stops or emergency maneuvers.
symptoms: the power steering and brakes become inoperable
the vehicle cannot be restarted due to the location of the restart switch.
